   Punch bags, combat sports outfits and equipment

Punch bags, combat sports outfits and equipment

   Judo, karate, Tae Kwon Do, boxing or kick boxing. Whatever your combat
   sport, Domyos has the product you need - judo outfit, dobok, boxing
   gloves, pads ... And for your work-outs, check out our range of punch
   bags in PVC or leather and our martial arts accessories.
