Punch bags and accessories

   Leather or fabric punch bags, shields, punch mitts. You'll find all the
   punch balls and accessories you need for your combat sports training,
   boxing, karate, Tae Kwon Do... Whether you're into boxing or kick
   boxing, you'll find the punch bag that's perfect for your combat sport
   among our models, which range from 20 to 38kg.
