   Boxing gloves and protective wraps

Boxing gloves and protective wraps

   Explore our range of boxing essentials, including boxing and
   self-defence gloves, punching bag gloves, wraps and mitts. Our range is
   for young and old alike, covering sizes 6 oz to 14 oz. Whether you
   practice occasionally or regularly, our selection offers boxing
   equipment tailored to your level.
